snippet.title: The Battle Cats Unite! - First Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Join over 350 variety of cats in The Battle Cats Unite! With over 300 stages to play including daily Blitz stages, there is so much to do – Gather your Cat army and rule the universe! Coming to you this 9th December 2021 on Nintendo Switch!
